            {

              "aggregationType": "Average",

Equal to counter Process\\PrivateBytes plus the size of memory-mapped data, ignoring any memory which was mapped or allocated by the xVelocity in-memory analytics engine (VertiPaq) in excess of the xVelocity engine Memory Limit.",

              "metricFilterPattern": "^\\b(?i)EM|P\\d$"

              "aggregationType": "Average",

              "unit": "Count",
              "aggregationType": "Average",
              "metricFilterPattern": "^\\b(?i)EM|P\\d$"

              "unit": "Count",
              "aggregationType": "Average",
              "metricFilterPattern": "^\\b(?i)EM|P\\d$"

            {
              "name": "ProcessingPoolIdleNonIOThreads",
              "displayName": "Threads: Processing pool idle non-I/O threads",

              "unit": "Count",
              "aggregationType": "Average",
              "metricFilterPattern": "^\\b(?i)EM|P\\d$"

            {
              "name": "QueryPoolIdleThreads",
              "displayName": "Threads: Query pool idle threads",
              "displayDescription": "Number of idle threads for I/O jobs in the processing thread pool.",
              "unit": "Count",
              "aggregationType": "Average",
              "metricFilterPattern": "^\\b(?i)EM|P\\d$"

              "displayDescription": "Number of busy threads in the short parsing thread pool.",
              "unit": "Count",
              "aggregationType": "Average",
              "metricFilterPattern": "^\\b(?i)EM|P\\d$"

              "unit": "Count",
              "aggregationType": "Average",
              "metricFilterPattern": "^\\b(?i)EM|P\\d$"

              "unit": "Count",
              "aggregationType": "Average",
              "metricFilterPattern": "^\\b(?i)EM|P\\d$"

              "name": "QueryDuration",

              "unit": "Milliseconds",
              "aggregationType": "Average",
              "metricFilterPattern": ""
            },
            {
              "name": "QueryPoolJobQueueLength",
              "displayName": "Threads: Query pool job queue length",
              "displayDescription": "Number of jobs in the queue of the query thread pool.",
              "unit": "Count",
              "aggregationType": "Average",
              "metricFilterPattern": ""
            }
          ]
        }

            {
              "name": "Engine",
              "displayName": "Engine",
              "blobDuration": "PT1H"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Microsoft.PowerBIDedicated/capacities/providers/Microsoft.Insights/diagnosticSettings/read",
